As we reflect on Negeri's endurance,

00:16:16.299 --> 00:16:19.740
we're reminded of all those who are currently

00:16:19.740 --> 00:16:24.019
in during persecution are in prison for their faith.

00:16:24.980 --> 00:16:28.139
Do your brothers and sisters in during persecution

00:16:28.139 --> 00:16:33.139
in Eritrea, Russia and in all other areas of the world

00:16:33.659 --> 00:16:38.659
we are praying for you and we love you very much.

